used on:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1199\">\n<li data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1048\">\n<p data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1048\">Featured snippet gaps for your keywords<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1112\">\n<p data-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1112\">\u201cPeople Also Ask\u201d question clusters relevant to your industry<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1113\" data-end=\"1162\">\n<p data-start=\"1115\" data-end=\"1162\">Local voice search queries in your service area<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1163\" data-end=\"1199\">\n<p data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1199\">Competitor snippet wins and losses<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1311\">This helps us target question formats and topics that Google already rewards, customised for the Kenyan market.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1313\" data-end=\"1433\">We also use tools like Ahrefs, SEMrush, and AlsoAsked to identify related questions your audience is actively searching.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1435\" data-end=\"1486\">3. Structured Content Creation and Reformatting<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1488\" data-end=\"1576\">Once opportunities are mapped out, we rewrite or enhance content with a clear structure:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1775\">\n<li data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1633\">\n<p data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1633\">Use of <code data-start=\"1587\" data-end=\"1593\">&lt;h2&gt;<\/code> and <code data-start=\"1598\" data-end=\"1604\">&lt;h3&gt;<\/code> subheadings in question form<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1634\" data-end=\"1681\">\n<p data-start=\"1636\" data-end=\"1681\">Short, direct paragraph answers (40\u201360 words)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1682\" data-end=\"1730\">\n<p data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1730\">Step-by-step lists or tables, where appropriate<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1731\" data-end=\"1775\">\n<p data-start=\"1733\" data-end=\"1775\">Internal linking between related questions<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1777\" data-end=\"1868\">We apply semantic structuring and topic modelling to match Google\u2019s language understanding.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1989\">If needed, we create entirely new blog posts or pillar pages designed to attract and capture voice and snippet results.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1991\" data-end=\"2026\">4. Schema Markup Implementation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2028\" data-end=\"2098\">We implement JSON-LD structured data using valid schema types such as:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2175\">\n<li data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2111\">\n<p data-start=\"2102\" data-end=\"2111\"><code data-start=\"2102\" data-end=\"2111\">FAQPage<\/code><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2112\" data-end=\"2121\">\n<p data-start=\"2114\" data-end=\"2121\"><code data-start=\"2114\" data-end=\"2121\">HowTo<\/code><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2122\" data-end=\"2133\">\n<p data-start=\"2124\" data-end=\"2133\"><code data-start=\"2124\" data-end=\"2133\">WebPage<\/code><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2134\" data-end=\"2145\">\n<p data-start=\"2136\" data-end=\"2145\"><code data-start=\"2136\" data-end=\"2145\">Article<\/code><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2146\" data-end=\"2157\">\n<p data-start=\"2148\" data-end=\"2157\"><code data-start=\"2148\" data-end=\"2157\">Product<\/code><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2158\" data-end=\"2175\">\n<p data-start=\"2160\" data-end=\"2175\"><code data-start=\"2160\" data-end=\"2175\">LocalBusiness<\/code><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2177\" data-end=\"2283\">This markup helps Google index your answers more accurately and makes your site eligible for rich results.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2285\" data-end=\"2544\">For WordPress sites, we integrate this either directly or through trusted schema plugins, depending on your CMS and theme structure. Explore our <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/website-maintenance-and-support-services-in-kenya\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" da