ds)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1191\" data-end=\"1295\">\n<p data-start=\"1193\" data-end=\"1295\">Align your content with Google\u2019s E-E-A-T (Experience, Expertise, Authority, Trustworthiness) standards<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1384\">\n<p data-start=\"1298\" data-end=\"1384\">Predict the types of content Google will likely feature in future AI-driven interfaces<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1386\" data-end=\"1430\">Editorial + Technical SEO Under One Roof<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1432\" data-end=\"1532\">Unlike agencies that separate copywriting and SEO, our team bridges both. This means we can deliver:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1534\" data-end=\"1725\">\n<li data-start=\"1534\" data-end=\"1604\">\n<p data-start=\"1536\" data-end=\"1604\">Structured, editorially sound content that reads well and ranks high<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1605\" data-end=\"1652\">\n<p data-start=\"1607\" data-end=\"1652\">Clean HTML and semantic markup implementation<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1653\" data-end=\"1725\">\n<p data-start=\"1655\" data-end=\"1725\">Advanced schema coding and error-free structured data across all pages<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1727\" data-end=\"1844\">We also handle audits, reformatting, CMS integration, and ongoing maintenance, streamlining your optimisation efforts.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"2008\">Explore our <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/website-redesign-services-in-kenya\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"1858\" data-end=\"1941\">Website Redesign services<\/a> if you want to rework your entire site with AEO-readiness in mind.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2010\" data-end=\"2068\">ROI-Driven Optimisation for Visibility and Conversions<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2070\" data-end=\"2142\">We approach AEO with measurable outcomes in mind\u2014not just rankings, but:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2144\" data-end=\"2345\">\n<li data-start=\"2144\" d