 marketers ask about AEO. If you\u2019re still unsure whether it\u2019s right for your brand, these insights should help clarify the value and scope.<\/div><\/div>[vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Is AEO just another word for SEO?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052221-d2dccac3-2f8e82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"646\"><strong data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"308\">No.<\/strong> While AEO is closely related to SEO, it focuses specifically on how content is structured and surfaced in <em data-start=\"415\" data-end=\"448\">non-traditional search features, <\/em>such as featured snippets, voice results, \u201cPeople Also Ask,\u201d and AI-generated summaries. Traditional SEO helps you rank in organic listings; AEO helps you become <em data-start=\"611\" data-end=\"623\">the answer<\/em> Google displays first.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"648\" data-end=\"772\">In other words, AEO optimises for visibility in <em data-start=\"696\" data-end=\"728\">zero-click search environments<\/em>, which are becoming more dominant in Kenya.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How long does it take to get featured in a snippet?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052312-795bf34f-889a82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"865\">It depends on several factors:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"867\" data-end=\"997\">\n<li data-start=\"867\" data-end=\"898\">\n<p data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"898\">How competitive your query is<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"899\" data-end=\"941\">\n<p data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"941\">The structure and clarity of your answer<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"942\" data-end=\"997\">\n<p data-start=\"944\" data-end=\"997\">Whether your content is already ranking in the top 10<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"999\" data-end=\"1176\">For most of our clients, we begin seeing snippet wins within <strong data-start=\"1060\" data-end=\"1077\">4 to 12 weeks<\/strong> after optimisation. Pages that already rank but lack structure often qualify faster once improved.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1272\">We monitor progress using Google Search Console, Ahrefs, and our in-house SERP tracking tools.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Will AEO help with my local SEO too?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361191995-ff8a0d69-1fe982d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1320\" data-end=\"1401\">Yes. Many voice searches and mobile queries in Kenya are local in nature\u2014such as:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1511\">\n<li data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1434\">\n<p data-start=\"1405\" data-end=\"1434\"><em data-start=\"1405\" data-end=\"1434\">\u201cBest car mechanic near me\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1435\" data-end=\"1467\">\n<p data-start=\"1437\" data-end=\"1467\"><em data-start=\"1437\" data-end=\"1467\">\u201cAffordable land in Malindi\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1468\" data-end=\"1511\">\n<p data-start=\"1470\" data-end=\"1511\"><em data-start=\"1470\" data-end=\"1511\">\u201cHow to register a business in Nairobi\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1513\" data-end=\"1763\">AEO helps your content rank for these by structuring it to align with how real users ask questions. When combined with proper local schema, Google Business Profile optimisation, and location-based content, it strengthens your local SEO significantly.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1765\" data-end=\"1909\">Learn more about our <a class=\"cursor-pointer\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/services\/local-seo-services-in-kenya\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"1786\" data-end=\"1861\">Local SEO services<\/a> and how they pair with AEO for full visibility.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Do I need new content or can we optimise existing pages?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361240947-6ed290f2-a03582d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1977\" data-end=\"2210\">Both options are available. In many cases, we begin by reformatting and enhancing your existing content, especially if it&#8217;s already ranking but not being featured. This is faster and more cost-effective than starting from scratch.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2396\">However, in competitive industries or for queries you\u2019re not currently targeting, new content creation may be necessary. We\u2019ll advise you on the right mix during our content audit.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How do I know if I already appear in PAA or snippets?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361291476-30b845c7-304f82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2461\" data-end=\"2690\">You can check manually by Googling your core questions and seeing if your website appears in featured snippets or \u201cPeople Also Ask\u201d sections. However, a full analysis requires tools like Google Search Console, Ahrefs, or SEMrush.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2692\" data-end=\"2847\">As part of our AEO service, we run a snippet and PAA audit for your site and track performance over time, including wins, losses, and new opportunities.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][\/vc_tta_accordion][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; type=&#8221;vc_default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;5&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;10&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716548610536{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column][vc_single_image image=&#8221;5242&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; lazy_loading=&#8221;true&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_colum